Package org.jlab.mya

Class DataNexus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlab.mya.DataNexus
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OnDemandNexus, PooledNexus
    public abstract class DataNexus
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the possibly multiple data sources required to service requests to a cluster of Mya hosts, which make up a deployment. A configuration file (Java properties) is required to be in the class path: "deployments.properties". If this file is not found this class will throw an ExceptionInInitializerError upon being loaded by the class loader.
